  <p class="sec-q">"What does marketing look like in person?"</p>
  <h2 class="sec-title">Events</h2>
  <p class="sec-sub">Bringing digital product strategy to in-person experiences at scale.</p>

  <div class="sec-stats">
    <div class="sec-stat-block">
