  <div class="sec-body-grid">
    <div class="sec-left">
      <p class="sec-text">Events aren't just logistics — they're the moment your digital messaging has to survive contact with a room full of real people. From AIESEC congresses to iConnections flagship events in Miami, New York, Singapore, and São Paulo, the best product marketing happens when the platform and the physical experience reinforce each other. Platform pavilions, product demos at scale, in-person campaign activations, and making thousands of allocators feel like they're at the center of something — all of it informs how I think about product marketing the rest of the year.</p>
      <div class="sec-links">
        <a href="https://open.spotify.com/episode/5GR96zDjiCwfrXnxaKrbDV" class="sec-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Messaging and events — podcast episode ↗</a>
